<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yasūʿu ạảʿ̊jib̊ biạs̊mihi .. ạản̊ʿim̊ biḥubĩhi ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 falaẙsa sẖakẖ̊ṣuⁿ gẖaẙrahu .. ạảḥabãnā ḥatãy̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V2]
 2- fāllhu jāʾa fī ạl̊jasad̊ .. waḥalã ạảẙḍaⁿạ baẙnanā
 wālnĩʿ̊maẗu wāl̊ḥaqũ qad̊ .. ṣārā bīasūʿa lanā

[V3]
 3- wafīhi kulũ niʿ̊maẗiⁿ .. badat̊ mina ạllhi lanā
 fāi̹nãhu ạảḥabãnā .. gẖasãlanā min̊ ại̹tẖ̊minā

[V4]
 4- wah̊wa raḥīmuⁿ kāhinuⁿ .. yar̊tẖī liman̊ qad̊ jurĩba
 lạảnãhu tajarãba .. wanaf̊sahu qad̊ wahaba

[V5]
 5- wah̊wa yarudũ naf̊sanā .. ại̹dẖ̊ kulã ḥīniⁿ yasẖ̊faʿu
 fālsẖũk̊ra wāl̊ḥam̊da lahu .. maʿa ạltẖãnāʾi nar̊faʿu

[V6]
 6- dẖik̊ru ạs̊mihi yaḥ̊lū lanā .. fīhi ạlsũrūru wāl̊ʿazā
 fī kulĩ ḥīniⁿ nar̊tajī .. majīyảhu mina ạlsãmā</lyrics>
<title>yswʿ ạ̉ʿjb bạsmh</title>
</song>